---
title: Indian Style Eggs Benedict and Buttery Naans With Mango Chutney Glazed Bacon and Gingery Veg
description: We love a good Eggs Benedict & Naans With Bacon &Veg and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ea2ffe80e69274b58143b4d-f0d53df1-af5ac056.jpg
